description: This file initializes the structural layout of a web application's user interface by inserting HTML markup for main containers like app shell, sidebar, header, and main content area into the DOM element with id 'app'. It defines a function 'initAppShell' that sets up the initial UI structure and calls it immediately.

methods.name: initAppShell()
methods.description: Creates the main structural UI components of the application and inserts them into the DOM element with id 'app'.
